        <h1>Safety</h1>
        <h2>A safe ammonium nitrate fertilizer</h2>
        
        <p>F<span class="umacr">&#362;</span>SN&trade; is a safe, technologically advanced ammonium nitrate fertilizer that enhances the agronomic benefits of the fertilizer and saves you time and effort.</p>

        <p>The fusing of nitrate and sulfate suppresses the detonability of the nitrate while adding improved agronomic benefits, including optimizing plant uptake potential. The fusion process suppresses nitrate potency, making the fertilizer easy to use and store. It&rsquo;s a safe source of nitrate that adds agronomic efficiency and operational flexibility. F<span class="umacr">&#362;</span>SN provides peace of mind and improved crop yields.</p>
    </article>
    
